{"tid":1217932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國大學開始share逃犯條例！","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T16:03:40.000Z","uid":67295,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db76b13a3fd316aa702fb818ba436d0b9c39401f","tid":1217932,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:26:34.000Z","msg":"好啦其實係我黎 不過見好多同學都想出分力 甚至到遊行有外國人支持我地<br />\n希望大家可以post係自己大學個page度 即使上唔到街 都令更多人留意同簽署<br />\n<br />\n唔知post邊放晒係學術台同時事台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsiudid.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgsiudid.png&h=80ee1cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJxSa4V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJxSa4V.png&h=41993feb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e6784d7dbec9980438a5a463a792fe63452212f","tid":1217932,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"716e268c078bea3e85ae58f22a8ec2b3b7f06c3d","tid":1217932,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:27:30.000Z","msg":"段文 啲link我都係reddit copy<br />\n香港加油！<br />\n<br />\n#noextraditionbill<br />\n<br />\nRegarding the protest in Hong Kong, it is still happening. Reading in the Legislative Council is scheduled every weekday until 24th June. I believe Hong Kong needs help from everywhere in the world. And I would be sincerely pleased if all of you could sign these petitions.<br />\n<br />\nThere are six white house petition right now.<br />\n<br />\n有人整理左全部屬於簽名既weblinks，希望大家share出去出一份力 thanks 🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n1⃣Reject Immigration or Non-Immigration Visas of Hong Kong Government Officials Violating Human Rights<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/reject-immigration-or-non-immigration-visas-hong-kong-government-officials-violating-human-rights\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Freject-immigration-or-non-immigration-visas-hong-kong-government-officials-violating-human-rights&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=13fc37e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/reject-immigration-or-non-immigration-visas-hong-kong-government-officials-violating-human-rights</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣Revoke the U.S. Citizenship and Visas of the Hong Kong and China Officials who are in Support of the Extradition Bill<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frevoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=cfa7c7b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill</a><br />\n<br />\n3⃣Extradition Law Amendment in Hong Kong &mdash; Threat to Personal Safety and Freedom<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=68ad3870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n4⃣全球聯署【反送中 民意不可欺 為香港企硬】Global Signing: Against Extradition to China<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/民間人權陣線-civil-human-rights-front-全球聯署-反送中-民意不可欺-為香港企硬-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%A3%E7%B7%9A-civil-human-rights-front-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%AC%BA-%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E7%A1%AC-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=8cb8b71f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/民間人權陣線-civil-human-rights-front-全球聯署-反送中-民意不可欺-為香港企硬-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china</a>"},{"pid":"69bbbe1bedd28026eef00f93bc7115fe2e5bd77b","tid":1217932,"uid":114186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"推到英國政府取消台獨之母777全家BC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1edd1fc82eb998f9a0295591fa47ba0353efa6a","tid":1217932,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:29:23.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"9d2b466c89f474d436c4902b4935ba9a35302888","tid":1217932,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38d631117eb02352a037df7f6cec4c9cfbe163b4","tid":1217932,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2e3b0dbabbe7a06061deb32dcfbbeca53e2e62c","tid":1217932,"uid":241424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"真I大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6e6dc44e696b9d612d50bb4c02e2eab4d572da","tid":1217932,"uid":240628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"[廣傳][長文]長期革命，每個人都要準備對抗催淚彈/胡椒噴霧必須用品<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/OeDsoU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/OeDsoU</a>"},{"pid":"a998e231d0b2a3d8c6be22f159ea199c3310daf8","tid":12